Q13.Write PHP script to read above created "book.xml" file into simpleXML object. 
Display attributes and elements.(Hint : simple_xml_load_file() function) 

Answer:::::::::::::::::::::::
<?php

$xml=simplexml_load_file("books1.xml");
foreach($xml->book as $b)
{
	echo "<br>Bookno: ".$b->bookno;
	echo "<br>Bookname: ".$b->bookname;
	echo "<br>Authorname: ".$b->authorname;
	echo "<br>Price: ".$b->price;
	echo "<br>Year: ".$b->year;
}
?>

